BBjGridExWidget.ContextMenu

Class BBjGridContextMenuPredefinedMenuitem

  • java.lang.Object
    • BBjGridExWidget.ContextMenu.BBjGridContextMenuPredefinedMenuitem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BBjGridContextMenuItemInteface

    public class BBjGridContextMenuPredefinedMenuitem
extends java.lang.Object
implements BBjGridContextMenuItemInteface
    A class which represents predefined menu items. The items are packed with the grid you can not change the icon of these items or add css classes to them. If you need to change the label any of these items then you need to do in the translation file.
    Author:
    Hyyan Abo Fakher
